53:30.040 --> 53:32.760
in your head or publicly for choosing something

53:32.760 --> 53:33.600
you didn't choose.

53:33.600 --> 53:35.960
And that is a slippery slope.

53:35.960 --> 53:37.840
Well, and you know, it's rare that you actually understand

53:37.840 --> 53:40.000
