53:51.400 --> 53:52.600
that Linux is gonna do a great job,

53:52.600 --> 53:54.000
but it's not always the right tool.

53:54.000 --> 53:55.960
And we shouldn't judge people for not using it.

53:55.960 --> 53:59.040
